quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,34,"Maaku : "Hara no e kafidii…ďe mon …ďen oon mb no fu…ó…óa tagoore refi o ruttita nde […ďaawo maayde]?" Maaku :"Ko Alla fu…ó…óata tagoore nde refti O ruttita nde Ko honno fefindara …óon [faade e meere]?""
  10,35,"Maaku : "Hara no e kafidii…ďe mon …ďeen on feewnoowo e goonga?" Maaku: "Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on peewnoowo e goonga …ďuri haandude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewanataa (hoore mon) si wanaa o feewna? Ko he…ďi on sifa no √Īaawirton?"
  10,36,"Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke …óen nafataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko ganndu…óo ko …ďe ngollata."
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaa fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde gooŇčginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka Jey…óo winndere nden."
  10,38,"Kaa …ďe mbiat : "o fekindi nde?" Maaku : "ngaddee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo kattan…óon ga Alla, si on laatike gooŇč…ďe"."
  10,39,"Ko woni, …ďe njeddii ko …ďe ku…ďindaaki ganndal mun, [ko …ďe fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araani …ďe taho. Ko wano non adinoo…ďe …ďen fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane too√Īoo…ďe …ďen wa'unoo."
  10,40,"No e ma…ď…ďe gooŇč…óin…óo nde, no e ma…ď…ďe kadi mo gooŇč…óinaa nde. Ko Joomi maa …ďuri anndude bonnoo…ďe …ďeen."
  10,41,"Si …ďe njeddii ma, maaku : "No woodani kam (njo…ďdi) golle am, no woodani on (njo…ďdi) golle mon. Onon ko on his…ďe ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi kis…óo ko ngolloton"."
  10,42,"No e ma…ď…ďe …ďeen he…óotoo…ďe ma. E ko annannta faa…óu …ďe …ďeen, hay tawii …ďe haqqiltah?"